<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٥١٦ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/549">إِسْحَاقُ: </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6555">النَّضْرُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2638">سُلَيْمَانَ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2809">أَبَا وَائِلٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1339">حُذَيْفَةَ </a>: <span class="c2">«﴿وَأَنْفِقُوا فِي سَبِيلِ اللهِ وَلا تُلْقُوا بِأَيْدِيكُمْ إِلَى التَّهْلُكَةِ﴾ قَالَ: نَزَلَتْ فِي النَّفَقَةِ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>